                    <div class="guide-item" id="introduction">
                        <h1>Introduction</h1>

                        <p>Cicero website is custom designed and developed website which allow admin to edit/update or add new information in the website using custom made <strong>Software Modules</strong>. there are total 10 modules in admin section.</p>
                        <h3>Used Technology</h3>
                        <p>
                        </p><ul>
                            <li>.Net core 2.1</li>
                            <li>C# 7</li>
                            <li>HTML 5</li>
                            <li>CSS 2 and CSS 3</li>
                            <li>JavaScript(jQuery)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p></p>

                        <h3>Server Requirement</h3>
                        <p>
                        </p><ul>
                            <li>C# 7 or Higher</li>
                            <li>IIS 10 or Higher</li>
                            <li>Latest SQlServer Database</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p></p>
                        <h3>Browser Compatibility</h3>
                        <p>
                        </p><ul>
                            <li>Google Chrome </li>
                            <li>Firefox</li>
                            <li>Internet Explorer 9+</li>
                            <li>Safari</li>
                            <li>Android Browser</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p></p>


