                                </a>
                                <i>Click on the above image to make it larger </i>
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div id="managerole">
                            <h3>Manage Roles</h3>
                            <p>This Module was developed to allow admin to Add/Edit/Delete roles and permissions for the user claims in Website.</p>
                            <p>
                                To view list of roles for users. The admin can also change the status or delete roles here.
                                <a href="~/userguide/managerole1.PNG" class="lightbox" target="_blank">
                                    <img src="~/userguide/managerole1.PNG" width="100%" />
                                </a>
                                The admin can also change the status or delete roles here.
                                <i>Click on the above image to make it larger </i>
