                                            <img src="~/userguide/managemenubottom.PNG" width="100%" />
                                        </a>

                                        <i>Click on the above image to make it larger </i>

                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>
                                Click save to save changes and delete to remove them

                                <a href="~/userguide/managemenu2.PNG" class="lightbox" target="_blank">
                                    <img src="~/userguide/managemenu2.PNG" width="100%" />
                                </a>
                                <i>Click on the above image to make it larger </i>
                            </p>
                            <ul class="ul-number user-guide-list">
                                <li><strong>Menu:</strong><p>The displayed title of the article can be changed here.</p></li>
                                <li><strong>Css Class:</strong><p>The admin can set the css class the article to use here.</p></li>
                                <li><strong>Short Description:</strong><p>A brief description or any related information about the article can be set here.</p></li>
                                <li><strong>Url:</strong><p>This is a unique identifier though which the article can be searched by in the url.</p></li>
                                <li><strong>Open in new Window?:</strong><p>Check this check box to open to a new window when the article link is clicked on the frontend.</p></li>
                                <li><strong>Delete:</strong><p>Click delete to delete a particular article from the menu. This will remove it from being displayed.</p></li>
                                <li><strong>Save:</strong><p>Click Save to make save changes.</p></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div id="managemedia">
